This is a sample Web Application project for  Continuous Integration/ Continous Deployment.
TOOLS used - Jenkins, Tomcat, Github, Sonarqube

Tomcat Instruction
Configure your tomcat-users.xml file so that your user has sufficient permissions to deploy.

<role rolename="manager-script"/>
<role rolename="manager-jmx"/>
<user username="tomcat" password="s3cret" roles="manager-script,manager-jmx"/>
<role rolename="admin-gui" />
<user username="admin" password="Nikkikutti123#" roles="manager-gui,admin-gui" />
--------BEFORE ENDING TAG

Configure sonarqube with required info
Create jenkins pipeline 
Add required plugins i.e sonarqube, deploy to war container
Add build tool maven 
Add sonarquber server and tool
Configure credentials

run pipeline


 

